Heart of Faydwer) now has several members that are high enough levels to begin going on Dragon Raids. <br>
<br>
First I would like to find out what requirements we to know in order to go on these raids i.e. level, items  etc..?<br>
<br>
Secondly how to sign-up for the raids, whether or not guild members of similar classes will be grouped together, and is there any senority when it comes to loot from these raids?<br>
<br>
