<br>
First off, check the FAQ off the front page (button on the left hand side of the page) for information on dragon raids. <br>
<br>
To sign up for the Dragon raid mailing list (a must), look above you on the forum. There is a form box talking about dragon raids. Put in your email address and when I send out an email warning people of when a dragon raid is coming, you'll get instructions in the email about how to sign up. <br>
<br>
Levels are: For all healers - 40+<br>
For all melee classes - 40+<br>
For all intelligence casters except enchanters - 45+<br>
For all enchanters - 40+<br>
For all bards - 40+<br>
<br>
We don't promise that we'll group guild members together. We make the groups based on who's there and on a certain strategy. <br>
<br>
There is no seniority on loot. The full loot rules are in a topic that I will bump to the top, as are the attendance rules. <br>
<br>
I'll put the event on the Calendar. Sat. March 24th, Zatriz is running a Mixer raid to Splitpaw for levels 36-45. Details are in the events forum. <br>
<br>
Haemish MacLennan<br>
Clan Chieftan<br>
The Silver Daggers<br>
